LAGOS – Peter Amuchie (Saint Peters), the Founder Creative Director of Drop Off Fashion, has released some of the 2023 collections of the clothing brand. This was seen on his social media page @saint.petersgram. Amuchie has been posting new designs from his brand with captions like “meet some of the 2023 collections for Drop Off fashion @dropoff.lagos designed by me.” The eye-catching outfits have attracted the attention of fashion enthusiasts all over social media spaces with heartwarming comments from the public.